<body>
    <h1>INC08672078=C2=A0- mfcgd\wasAPIMprod credential expiry</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"c7e13c826a08"><strong>PRB00024864 </strong>- <strong=
>INC08672078</strong>&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"aee0f4841c5d">Technical / Immediate Fix:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"507f925b0938">
<li local-id=3D"24d3436d61b5">
<p local-id=3D"cba841141e7c">Communication via the ING APIM for SCV, MLK, P=
AW, and SSW resumed at 10:06am HKT after GAM team reset password for mfcgd\=
wasAPIMprod account that expired last June 27, 2026.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7d85701359c9"><strong>Mfcgd\wasAPIMprod&nbsp;=3D /S/108078/M=
LI/Hirooka, Kinue (backup) /S/490766/MLI/Yeung, Rosalina</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"b77182eedb89"></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"a5=
05fdf0-cba1-40e5-ad36-c2e9cfe80e8d" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"015b0435-f5a1-403c-b250-9664e6843d78">
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f5f5f5" data-local-id=3D"82f85be5-303e-4dac-a=
