nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"92fa5b155228">No clear accountable owner for that ID</p></td=
>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5bef5984-58f8-430a-9938-996cc3c3a3f1">
<td data-local-id=3D"87f064a7-bf04-48c0-9503-43bee42e2871" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d101e56d93ce"><strong>Response</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"fc492401-9f07-496a-a13f-d1149258c5d1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ab73646d425a">No enforced action / escalation when ignored</=
p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"9b666d99ddc6"></p>
<p local-id=3D"fe5beb750d41">I am confirming the following with CyberArk PA=
S operations (Dennis Icaro)</p>
<p local-id=3D"21687a438aba">CyberArk Hub&nbsp;:: <a class=3D"external-link=
" href=3D"https://mfc.sharepoint.com/sites/CYB/SitePages/How-to-release-loc=
ked-accounts.aspx" rel=3D"nofollow">How to Release Locked Accounts</a></p>
<h3 local-id=3D"372b6e518afd" id=3D"INC08672078-mfcgd\wasAPIMprodcredential=
expiry-A.Account-levelvalidation">A. Account-level validation</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"bd59d2df-69c8-4857-a71c-ef6b8204e78e">
<li local-id=3D"0c4afe9e-868c-456a-9658-062bcd025625">
<p local-id=3D"1e65a65f4037">Is <code>mfcgd\wasAPIMprod</code> managed in C=
yberArk? <strong>It is onboarded as Semi-managed (SSEMI) in CyberArk, pleas=
e see </strong><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://mfc.sharepoint.co=
m/sites/CYB/SitePages/How-to-Change-Password-for-Unmanaged-and-Semi-Managed=
-Platforms.aspx" rel=3D"nofollow"><strong>How to Change Password for Unmana=
ged and Semi Managed Platforms</strong></a><strong> to understand how Semi-=
Managed platform works</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9c85063e-2e88-4e83-a878-373d7d1740f0">
<p local-id=3D"18f6305d9c9c">Which <strong>safe / vault / platform</strong>=
 is it stored under? <strong>Safe is NH_MLJ_ITIS_SUPP_S. Platform is NH_WIN=
DOM_SSEMI_DOMAINREC_DC_NoAAM, SSEMI =3D Semi-Managed</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"52f437b3-1a2f-4582-8a7c-fb773e5ebb4e">
<h3 local-id=3D"59c62a1e0b6f" id=3D"INC08672078-mfcgd\wasAPIMprodcredential=
expiry-B.Expiryconfiguration">B. Expiry configuration</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"e56de03c-0183-4944-8dc6-c138980ac64f">
<li local-id=3D"6aa8fb70-927d-406f-99d1-a1e152caed40">
<p local-id=3D"4c3f007afd3a">What is the configured:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"1c7fd1eb1ed6">
<li local-id=3D"1dbc2936-4233-425c-964e-fe72a7050c84">
<p local-id=3D"7253930b4a02">Password rotation policy? Should be rotated by=
 safe NH_MLJ_ITIS_SUPP_S Password Managers (PWMGR) since this is SSEMI</p><=
/li>
</ul></li>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
