lobal Access Management Team (</strong><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"m=
ailto:Information_Security@manulife.com" rel=3D"nofollow"><strong>Informati=
on_Security@manulife.com</strong></a><strong>) to confirm</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"27efd372-de03-46f0-90fe-8ddb905cee38">
<p local-id=3D"9381d7b30a33">Safe owner - <strong>Kinue Hirooka</strong></p=
></li>
